snippet.textDisplay: Seems Coke studio is losing it's signature identity, now the song is becoming an item of watching rather than listening, in some cases it's as if putting the OLD wine in NEW bottles.... I'm not disagreeing some other coke studio 1songs where some song's music and composition was international level and standard, this has been now the scope and platform to highlight our own charisma, expertise of people ie music maestros to the world to let them know who we are and what resources we have to enrich this Music industry...but sorry to say some cheap composition and music again reminds us that's why Hero Alom is famous here in BD...pls maintain or even surpass the benchmark of Coke studio's signature with our legendary performance and expertise in music, that may reintroduce who the Tigers are and for why they are famous for...
